####创建Arrrow文件需要geneAnnotation(from gtf),genomeAnnotation(from BSgenome)，Fragments文件；三者染色体名称，染色体长度均要保持一致
``` R
arrowFiles <- createArrowFiles(
  inputFiles = "/jdfsbjcas1/ST_BJ/P21Z28400N0234/wangning12/1_project/3_2509riceLunchBreak/ATAC/data/A251113004/fragments_trimmed.tsv.gz",
  sampleNames = "A251113004",
  minTSS = 1,
  minFrags = 1000,
  excludeChr = c("Mt", "Pt"),
  addTileMat = TRUE,
  addGeneScoreMat = TRUE,
  subThreading = FALSE,   # 改回FALSE
  geneAnnotation = geneAnnotation,
  genomeAnnotation = genomeAnnotation
)
```



